    • getAs

      <T> T getAs(Class<T> platformClass)
      Gets the underlying platform-specific world object. This is an escape hatch to access platform-specific APIs.
      Type Parameters:
      T - The type of the platform-specific world.
      Parameters:
      platformClass - The class of the platform-specific world object (e.g., org.bukkit.World.class).
      Returns:
      The platform-specific world object, or null if the type is incompatible.
